)attr default(%+_)
  _ type( input) intens(low ) just(left ) hilite(uscore)
  ~ type(text) intens(high) caps(off) just(asis ) hilite(reverse) color(turq)
  [ type(output) intens(high) caps(off) just(left) pas(on) skip(on)
)Body Expand(\\)
%Tutorial -\-\~The z ISPF Git Interface (zigi)%\-\- Tutorial
%Selection ===>_ZCMD                                                          +
+
                                 %SET+
+
%SET+configures default values for the current repository:
+
%*+Configure the default Add All option on a Commit.
+
%*+Configure the default push option on a Commit.
+
%*+Configure a userid to be set for all PDS Members that will be set at Commit.
+  The userid is updated prior to Commit.
+
+The repository's z/OS dataset HLQ may be changed with the requirement that
+the number of qualifiers remain the same as the previous HLQ.
+
+Turn off, or on, prompting for file extensions when adding a PDS.
+
+Add the zginstall.rex generic installation script to the repository.
+
         +Press the%Enter+key to continue your ZIGI tutorial journey.
)Init
 .cursor  = &zcmd
)PROC
 &zcont = zigihsnp
)END
